data.description: YOUR FOREVER HOME IS HERE! Stately 3-story home with all the bells and whistles. Beat the summer heat with an icy cocktail in the backyard under the pergola, enjoy s'mores around the firepit, or cook your favorite meal in the outdoor kitchen. Inside, the open concept main level seamlessly connects the family room & kitchen for easy entertaining. The kids will enjoy 3rd floor game room/bedroom & adjacent theater. Down one flight, the master suite is a retreat, complete with a sitting area & well-appointed bath with his and her closets. Located in the South Wind Community near schools, shopping, entertainment & more!
